|year=2007
|title=Silman's Complete Endgame Course: From Beginner to Master
|url=https://archive.org/details/silmanscompletee00silm|publisher=Siles Press
|isbn=1-890085-10-3
|page=[https://archive.org/details/silmanscompletee00silm/page/n490 477]
|ref=harv
|postscript=<!--None-->}}</ref>根据Chessmetrics的排名，1912年至1914年间鲁宾斯坦的排名曾达到世界第一。<ref>[http://chessmetrics.com/cm/CM2/Summary.asp?Params=190510SSSSS3S000000000000111000000000000010100 Chessmetrics Summary for 1905–15] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120502183109/http://chessmetrics.com/cm/CM2/Summary.asp?Params=190510SSSSS3S000000000000111000000000000010100 |date=2012-05-02 }}, retrieved on 25-Apr-2007</ref>他与拉斯克曾约定于1914年举行[[国际象棋世界冠军|世界冠军]]对抗赛，但最终因[[第一次世界大战|第一次世界大战]]爆发而未能进行。<ref>{{Harvnb|Silman|2007|p=477}}</ref>

